<br>
at 50<br>
stealth 40<br>
blades 3<br>
Piercing 37<br>
envenom 29<br>
Cd 7<br>
CS 44<br>
<br>
or could reverse blades and piercing <br>
at lvl 14 i am currently<br>
stealth 10<br>
blades 2<br>
piercing 10<br>
envenom 4<br>
cd 4<br>
cs 10<br>
<br>
now other other NS on my server have stated if they allowed a respec they would go blades in retro spect.  the claim that  with 36 blades vs 36 pierce they would get an increase of about 100 points in damage  when using PA.  Also they claim that higher lvl dropped blades, have low speeds similar to the mines rapiers, and better stats, and you could dual wield proccing weapons..<br>
<br>
I would like some responses form other experienced rogues on this matter.  I tested out some blades with my NS.  Bastard sword was too slow for PVe, longsword was close, falcata identical to my rapier.  I am currently wielding rapier in main and falcata in off hand.  I have some high level piercers in my vault and a harvester of malign doom also.  So will the higher level bladed weapons make it worth it to spec blades ( with the incvreased damage)?  It seems to me that the piercieng styles are more suited to rogues than blades.   ANyway i would like some input on this matter.  HELP!!?<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uayraunderfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayra Underfoot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/31/02 12:23:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1979.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://haskett.dhs.org/ayraicon2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help!! blades or pierce? for Nightshade</span><hr size=1> If i could respec I would go into blades.  At lvl 33 i have 17 in pierce, but I don't even use piercing weaps at the moment (need to buy a player crafted one since i havent found a thrust drop in 10 levels).<br>
<br>
<br>
The pestilence sickle (cons yellow)  that i use gives: +blades, +celtic dual, proc's for 2x my dd spell and has dps: 10 (10 something) with a delay of 2.8 sec, and is left hand useable.<br>
<br>
Jewel Encrusted Claw (cons red)  (cant remember exact name, found it in Cour. Mines) gives: +blades, +celtic dual, proc's for 2x my dd spell and has dps: 12 or 13 with a delay of 2.6, i think this is left handed as well.<br>
<br>
now, i do more damage with these then I do with the only thrust weapons i have (2 rib ticklers, that con green =/ )  I'm going to buy a new set of player made daggers to see if it will help me out.. but i sure wish I would of went with blades =/ <p>---------------<Br>
