<a href="http://www.greypathfinders.com/daoc.htm">Glas Cinneadh</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uannid.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Anni D</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/31/02 11:17:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1979.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help!! blades or pierce? for Nightshade</span><hr size=1> Good news.<br>
<br>
Piercer found today in Bog.<br>
<br>
(calling from memory..)<br>
<br>
was something like 16 dps (point something)<br>
and 2.5 delay.<br>
 ***OFF HAND USEABLE***<br>
<br>
